    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdministrationInterface
    Services for managing movies from the administrator's point of view.
    Artist
    Represents an artist who has worked on a movie.
    ArtistManager
    Manages all the artists.
    Genre
    Set of movie genres.
    Location
    Represents a location where users can rent movies and leave reviews.
    LocationAdmin
    Represents the administration of the location.
    Movie
    Represents a movie.
    MovieManager
    Manages all the movies.
    NotLoggedInException
    Exception thrown when there is a problem with a user's account or their login.
    PersonalInformation
    Description of a person's personal information: identity, age, and address.
    RentingException
    Exception thrown when there is a problem during the rental of a movie by a user.
    Reservation
    Represents a reservation made by a user for a movie.
    ReservationManager
    Manages all the reservations.
    Review
    Represents a review made by a user for a movie.
    ReviewManager
    Manages all the reviews.
    User
    The User class represents a user.
    UserInterface
    Movie rental services from the user's point of view.
    UserManager
    Manages all the users.
